lead_paragraph: The Crimson Tide, who finally won over the last holdout Associated Press poll voter, have displayed remarkable consistency since Nick Saban became their coach.

headline.print_headline: Alabama, All Alone, Unscathed at the Top
headline.main: Unanimous No. 1 Alabama Perpetuates a Standard of Excellence

snippet: The Crimson Tide, who finally won over the last holdout Associated Press poll voter, have displayed remarkable consistency since Nick Saban became their coach....
abstract: Marc Tracy On College Football column considers undefeated and unanimous No. 1 Alabama's continuing dominance of college football, after weekend which saw three other top four teams lose; argues even if team loses national title, program's success over past decade has been unparalleled.
